data.description: Beautiful 5 year old Pulte built 4 bedroom, 3.5 bedroom home located in desirable River Crest Subdivision. It features hardwood floors downstairs with a formal dining room, gourmet kitchen with a new refrigerator, stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, an oversized island, a wine nook. An adjoining breakfast area compliments the family room which has a gas fireplace. Easily accessible from the kitchen/ family room is a screened in porch. There is an office/library on the main floor. Upstairs there is a bonus room, perfect for a media/game/tv room. The oversized Primary Suite includes his and her closets and separate tub/ shower. The secondary bedrooms also have large closets. The is an in-law bedroom with its on full bath upstairs. The HVAC is new. It has new lighting, a new Smart home system. There is a playground set in the backyard that will stay. The private backyard has a custom built wrought iron fence and patio grilling with a gas line. The 2 car garage connects to the house with a mud room. There are 2 separate heat pumps for efficiency.
